\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d41277c5c300aa582c4d6538ef25c15839f9c15","tid":2093382,"uid":152114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T21:22:31.000Z","msg":"我條鞋帶鬆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QL3T2Nzcqcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQL3T2Nzcqcs&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=d34045cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QL3T2Nzcqcs</a>"},{"pid":"b711583b1b3ff60a072d93af0d58c02f39b98ff6","tid":2093382,"uid":17794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T21:30:16.000Z","msg":"出生於香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fe1cc75debe9e642b1bbe27b7f58763fd11417","tid":2093382,"uid":197942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T21:33:29.000Z","msg":"唔知點解要生存<br />\n唔知點解會出現喺到<br />\n然後用幾十年建立既一切同而家所「擁有」既最終都會化灰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9595b781bcf40473a32f1f61e364f1b3bc5ca6f","tid":2093382,"uid":129660,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T22:46:40.000Z","msg":"首先自己所有野都below average<br />\n個人又敏感又悲觀 改唔到<br />\n未來只會有更多既悲傷，苦澀，痛楚等住自己"},{"pid":"dc506ee56c2ba9c40f2cf63ca0b86e9a9f83e7d7","tid":2093382,"uid":215026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T22:48:01.000Z","msg":"Same<br />\n覺得自己人生好可悲"},{"pid":"cbb7640a49fa24e34e45ade2cfe89403b35fd9c9","tid":2093382,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T22:51:22.000Z","msg":"「真正嚴肅的哲學問題只有一個，那就是自殺」<br />\n&mdash;卡繆"},{"pid":"79eaeb63bc5cb0fbd419aa4055ab2373bb47e551","tid":2093382,"uid":149981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"讀書又讀得唔好<br />\n興趣專長都半桶水咁<br />\n友情愛情全部破裂<br />\n屋企人又藍又難溝通<br />\n香港依家又咁樣<br />\n老實講見唔到有未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3e8f46528969caa33f63ad81b7ee9cb7b38a5c","tid":2093382,"uid":261700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:43:23.000Z","msg":"讀書唔叻,屋企有D錢但屋企人都想你快D畢業經濟獨立<br />\n而家只知道大把西工等住我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1ed28727baa7cc07ca90e3322a3e46f60723dd","tid":2093382,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:02:41.000Z","msg":"短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0131bbed2569ece3cbfd0f0a96d3eca2eb1c3f54","tid":2093382,"uid":22409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"1）預計之後嘅人生會好痛苦<br />\n2）工作壓力大 無前途<br />\n3）搵唔到人生意義 生存動力<br />\n4）唔想有煩惱"},{"pid":"6ec5608e34e587cac751ac37e366a8dbc5085994","tid":2093382,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78fe5cb3ef45a951b1ad7a6b7bbc77e99ced4118","tid":2093382,"uid":225549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T19:58:44.000Z","msg":"讀書無天份 唔知自己既興趣係乜<br />\n又比朋友背叛<br />\n你愛既人唔愛你<br />\n同屋企人有洪溝 完全溝通唔到<br />\n感覺人生已經冇任何意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站       <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=1112999f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>      。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"fc645bafda31c97b971a083cb33a8d400f7bfbd8","tid":2093382,"uid":225549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"